front.title: •Incom Corporation
front.gametext: Deploy on a Rebel Base interior site. Your ability-1 permanent pilots aboard T-16s, T-47s, Z-95s and X-wings (except squadrons) are replaced by ability-2 permanent pilots who add 1 to power. Canceled if opponent controls this site. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: Incom's core design team defected to the Alliance with the plans for the famed X-wing fighter. Once with the Alliance, many former Incom test pilots flew for the Rebellion.

pulledBy: We Wish To Board At Once
